\v 2 Cˀoi⁴qui³tso²: Ti⁴cˀa³ntjai³yao³ cjoa⁴fa³ˀai³tsjen³-no³, nca⁴ je³nčhoa¹ ma³čhian³ cjoa⁴te¹xo³ma³-le⁴ ncˀa³jmi³.  
