\s1 Nˀai³-le⁴ ntˀia³ xi³ vˀa³sje³-ni³ cjoa⁴nchi⁴na¹-le⁴ cjoa⁴ xi³ cho⁴tse⁴, cˀoa⁴ cjoa⁴ xi³ jchi¹nca³ 
