\s1 Jesús li²coi³ tsa³ˀya³xcon¹ ya⁴ Nazaret 
\r (Mr. 6:1-6; Lc. 4:16-30) 
\p  
\v 53 Cˀoi⁴ coan³ nca³ je³je³tˀa³cao⁴ je² cjoa⁴xco¹son²-vi⁴ Jesús, ja³ˀa³-ni³ ya⁴-ve⁴.  
