\v 1 Cˀia⁴ tjin¹ cˀa³ cho⁴ta⁴ scribano cao⁴ cho⁴ta⁴ fariseos xi³ tsˀe⁴ Jerusalén, xi³ ji³cho²con³-le⁴ Jesús, qui³tso²-le⁴:  
\v 2 A¹-ni³ nca³ si¹qui³tson¹-si¹ni³ cho⁴ta⁴-li⁴ costumbre-le⁴ cho⁴ta⁴jchi¹nca³, nca³ tsi² va³ne¹jon³ ntsja³ cˀia⁴ nca³ cjen² nio⁴.  
