\v 1 Cˀia⁴ ji³cho²con³-le⁴ cho⁴ta⁴ fariseos cao⁴ cho⁴ta⁴ saduceos, nca³ chˀao³ si⁴²cao⁴, qui³si³je¹-le⁴ nca³ coa⁴co²jnco³-le⁴ choa⁴ ya⁴ ncˀa³jmi³.  
\v 2 To⁴nca³ Jesús qui³nchja⁴-nca¹ni³: Cˀia⁴ nca³ je³ma³xon² nca³ ni⁴čhjin³, jon²-vi⁴ vi³xon¹³: Nta³ chon³ nchaon³, nca⁴ ni² chon³ ncˀa².  
\v 3 Cˀoa⁴ nca³ ta⁴njion²: Ntˀai⁴ cˀoa⁴ jtsi¹, nca⁴ yo³jvi³jma² cjoan³ xi³ ncha³ ncˀa², cˀoa⁴ ni² chon³ ncˀa². Xi³ cho⁴ta⁴jao²ncjain¹ ˀmi²-no³, ma³-no³ cho¹tˀa³ jo³ ma³ chon³ ncˀa², to⁴nca³ choa⁴-le⁴ ni⁴čhjin³ li²coi³ ma³-no³.  
\v 4 Je² cho⁴ta⁴ xi³ ntˀai⁴ tjio¹, xi³ tsˀen⁴-ni¹, xi³ to⁴si¹cha³jnqui³, si¹je¹ choa⁴, to⁴nca³ choa⁴ li²coi³ cˀoai⁴-le⁴, to⁴je² choa⁴-le⁴ Jonás xi³ qui³nchja⁴ya³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ Ni³na¹. Cˀoa⁴ Jesús qui³si³ca³tio¹ cho⁴ta⁴, qui³-ni³. 
\s1 Je² na⁴ˀyo⁴san³ xi³ tsˀe⁴ cho⁴ta⁴ fariseos cao⁴ cho⁴ta⁴ saduceos 
\r (Mr. 8:14-21) 
\p  
\v 5 Cˀoa⁴ ja³ˀai³ cho⁴ta⁴-le⁴ xi³ncoa³tˀa³ nta¹chi³con³, qui³cha³jin³-le⁴ nio⁴xti²la⁴.  
\v 6 Jesús qui³tso²-le⁴: Cho¹tsaon³, ti⁴coi²nta⁴-lao⁴³ yao³-no³ je² na⁴ˀyo⁴san³ xi³ tsˀe⁴ cho⁴ta⁴ fariseos cao⁴ cho⁴ta⁴ saduceos.  
