\v 16 To⁴nca³ tsa² tsi² cjoi⁴nčhˀoe¹-li², ca²tji³cao⁴-li² tsa² jnco³ tsa² jao², jme¹-ni³ nca³ si⁴²qui²xi⁴ya³nta³-ni³ nca³yi³je³ en¹-le⁴, tsa² jao², cˀoa⁴ tsa² jan² testigo.  
