\v 1 Nca⁴ je² cjoa⁴te¹xo³ma³-le⁴ ncˀa³jmi³ ma³nco¹son² jo³-ni³ tsa² jnco³ xi³ nˀai³-le⁴ ntˀia³, xi³ ji³tjo³ nca³ ta⁴njion²ya³ nca³ qui³ ca³jnqui³ cho⁴ˀnta³ xi³ si⁴²xa¹cao⁴ tso³jmi²ntje²-le⁴. 
