\p  
\v 20 Cˀia⁴ na⁴-le⁴ xti³-le⁴ Zebedeo ji³cho²con³-le⁴ Jesús, cao³ xti³-le⁴, tsa³ca³sen²xco¹nchˀin³tˀa³-le⁴ nca³ tjin¹ xi³ qui³si³je¹-le⁴.  
\v 21 Cˀoa⁴ Jesús qui³tso²-le⁴: Jme¹ xi³ me³-li². Qui³tso²: Cˀoa⁴-si¹ nca³ ca²ta³tio² je² jao² xti³-na⁴, jnco³ xi³ nca³qui²xi⁴-li⁴, cˀoa⁴ nqui²jnco³ xi³ nca³scon¹-li⁴ ya⁴ cjoa⁴te¹xo³ma³-li⁴.  
