\v 42 Jo¹ vi³xon¹³ xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ Cristo. ˀya¹ tsˀe⁴ ˀnti¹-le⁴. Cho⁴ta⁴ fariseos qui³tso²-le⁴ Jesús: Tsˀe⁴ David.  
\v 43 Cˀia⁴ Jesús qui³tso²-le⁴: Jo¹-sˀin²ˀni³ nca³ David qui³tso²-le⁴ Nai³-na⁴ cˀia⁴ nca³ to⁴tˀa³tsˀe⁴ Espíritu Santo qui³nchja⁴, nca⁴ tso²:  
\v 44 Je² Nai³-na¹ qui³tso²-le⁴ je² Nai³-na⁴: Ti⁴jna³tˀa³-nai¹³ nca³ qui²xi⁴-na⁴ sa³ˀnta³ nca³ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² si³cˀe¹yoa³ co²ntran⁴-li⁴ ya⁴nqui³ ntso⁴coi³.  
